This contains a list of banks in Norway . There are three types of banks in Norway: commercial banks , savings banks ( Norwegian : Sparebank) and branches of foreign banks. The list is complete as of October 2006.
The Financial Supervisory Authority of Norway Registry of Financial Institutions
